<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Self-help Toolkits - VibingSG</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <h2 style="color: #7b2ff7;">Self-help Toolkits</h2>
    <p>Explore curated articles and tools to support your mental wellness and academic success.</p>
    <div class="toolkits-grid">

      <div class="toolkits-card">
        <img src="/images/Breathe.png" alt="Deep Breathing" class="toolkits-thumb">
        <div class="toolkits-content">
          <div class="toolkits-title">Deep Breathing</div>
          <div class="toolkits-desc">Practice calm breathing exercises with this interactive tool from Calm.</div>
          <a href="https://www.calm.com/breathe" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Open Breathe →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="toolkits-card">
        <img src="/images/Timer.png" alt="Pomodoro Counter" class="toolkits-thumb">
        <div class="toolkits-content">
          <div class="toolkits-title">Pomodoro Timer</div>
          <div class="toolkits-desc">Use the Pomodoro timer to boost your focus and productivity.</div>
          <a href="https://pomodorotimer.online/" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Open Timer →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="toolkits-card">
        <img src="/images/Chatbot.png" alt="Chat with a Bot" class="toolkits-thumb">
        <div class="toolkits-content">
          <div class="toolkits-title">Chat with a Bot</div>
          <div class="toolkits-desc">Have a confidential chat with a wellbeing bot to explore your emotions.</div>
          <a href="https://mindline.sg/youth/assessment?wysa-tool-id=default" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Open Chat →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="toolkits-card">
        <img src="/images/StressMgmt.png" alt="Stress Management" class="toolkits-thumb">
        <div class="toolkits-content">
          <div class="toolkits-title">Stress Management</div>
          <div class="toolkits-desc">Read practical strategies for managing stress from trusted local resources.</div>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.mindline.sg/youth/article/coping-with-stress?type=mood" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Coping with Stress</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.ncss.gov.sg/research-and-insights/community-resources/mental-well-being/for-youths" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Mental Well-being for Youths</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.mindline.sg/youth/article/building-resilience-in-singapores-youth?type=interest" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Building Resilience</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="toolkits-card">
        <img src="/images/ExamTips.png" alt="Exam Preparation Tips" class="video-thumb">
        <div class="toolkits-content">
          <div class="toolkits-title">Exam Preparation Tips</div>
          <div class="toolkits-desc">Top strategies to study smart, reduce anxiety, and ace your exams.</div>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.topuniversities.com/student-info/health-and-support/exam-preparation-ten-study-tips" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Top 10 Study Tips</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://blog.cambridgeinternational.org/tips-for-effective-exam-preparation/" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Effective Exam Preparation</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.psb-academy.edu.sg/blog/study-tips-how-to-be-exam-ready" target="_blank" class="watch-link">How to be Exam-Ready</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="toolkits-card">
        <img src="/images/Time%20Management.png" alt="Time Management" class="toolkits-thumb">
        <div class="toolkits-content">
          <div class="toolkits-title">Time Management Tips</div>
          <div class="toolkits-desc">Learn to organize your time better with proven productivity techniques.</div>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://todoist.com/productivity-methods/pomodoro-technique" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Pomodoro Technique</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.skillsyouneed.com/ps/time-management.html" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Essential Time Management</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.mindtools.com/pages/main/newMN_HTE.htm" target="_blank" class="watch-link">Time Management Tools</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
